{"tid":1377342,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"前線：企位保持一米距離，冇心理準備咪撚企前面","createTime":"2019-07-28T13:37:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T17:36:08.000Z","uid":91753,"like":117,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"4d2923d7cf52d9cc9a6ba8a8136e92a53dde85e2","tid":1377342,"uid":91753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T13:37:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">情景：</span><br />\n<br />\n西區警署中聯辦前線死咗十幾個兄弟<br />\n<br />\n速龍一出，冇被捕準備嘅人發左癲咁向後退<br />\n<br />\n情況極為混亂，大家都異常恐懼<br />\n<br />\n而中場推後退得極慢<br />\n<br />\n嚴重影響前方撤離<br />\n<br />\n有兄弟跌落地<br />\n<br />\n四隻速龍㩒住一個。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">解決方法：</span><br />\n<br />\n儘量騰出周邊位置，至少一米<br />\n<br />\n真勇武人士全部守前線<br />\n<br />\n熱褲女仔請企中後場，唔好企喺前面阻礙義士後撤<br />\n<br />\n如果冇心理準備，唔好企喺前面。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">今日死十幾個兄弟，因為你班撚樣<br />\n光復香港 時代革命</span></span><br />\n<br />\n發夢內容。"},{"pid":"3018a92550f68b856320394d1a8eb7fcf4e835cd","tid":1377342,"uid":91753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T13:40:05.000Z","msg":"一米"},{"pid":"79830632183b1a21c288dd374d5f8780419298c6","tid":1377342,"uid":31796,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T13:41:58.000Z","msg":"今日冇發夢<br />\n但的確早幾次發夢都有班根本冇準備過嘅人企最前線"},{"pid":"383047e33a715dee467bc372bf2e6b314100dfe6","tid":1377342,"uid":91753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"79830632183b1a21c288dd374d5f8780419298c6","tid":1377342,"uid":31796,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T13:41:58.000Z","msg":"今日冇發夢<br />\n但的確早幾次發夢都有班根本冇準備過嘅人企最前線"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T13:50:05.000Z","msg":"出龍，就走難咁走"},{"pid":"ca21b3eb4d8be3f105f615365132059cac8b5d7e","tid":1377342,"uid":91753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T13:51:08.000Z","msg":"一米距離"},{"pid":"e7ca8874dc9e4c36c58a437425bf5717b19c6b78","tid":1377342,"uid":116529,"like":1,"dislik